'''Jade City''' is a "spot on the road" in northwestern [[British Columbia]], [[Canada]], located on [[British Columbia provincial highway 37|B.C. highway 37]], west of [[Good Hope Lake, British Columbia|Good Hope Lake]] and close to [[Cassiar, British Columbia|Cassiar]].

Two local seasonally-operated businesses offer highway services and sell [[jade]] products made from nearby formations of the stone.

